snippet.title: Sniper Assault (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Recorded with Elgato Game Capture HD from a real PS2 console using Composite cables. Game runs at 50 fps PAL standard with no alternative options. Video was resized 2x in Sony Vegas while preserving original aspect ratio. Original resolution is 720x576 interlaced.

As far as I know this game was only released in Europe and Japan. No US release.

Walkthrough Playthrough Gameplay
